---
title: American Popcorn Chicken with Smokey Aioli | Serves 2
description: Crsipy nuggets of popcorn chicken are always a fan favourite. Crunchy and golden on the outside, juicy and tender on the
inside, does it get much better? Maybe with a smokey aioli dip it can!
